  "detailed_description": "由朵游社联合Fantasia Studio共同开发的恐怖解谜游戏《FALL坠落之后》即将登陆STEAM！希望大家能够喜欢~<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/636f7b886c5b3a4ae9d3c3d48eee7cc7.avif?t=1680426984\" width=420 height=80 /></span><br>小红和小蓝是一对要好的朋友，一次意外使她们从山崖坠落。再次醒来时，周围尽是恐怖的怪物、凄凉的白骨，到处都是危险的陷阱……她们能否成功逃离？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/dbb189b52fbad2d247ebe1be99008c29.avif?t=1680426984\" width=420 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/1aaa01e5542e5aa1dd2cec26babcc9a4.avif?t=1680426984\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/6486fdc706bc2837ace072e310a4f5f1.avif?t=1680426984\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/4ef957fa42655fa1a30058170d662ffa.avif?t=1680426984\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/6eccac10e1332e75e7bd6f57d2e3a133.avif?t=1680426984\" width=420 height=80 /></span><br>游戏以调查解谜为主，根据不同的选择可以达成3种不同的结局，决定着主人公的命运。<br>限时的设计，让体验更加紧张刺激！<br>单周目游戏时长在1~2个小时，放心食用。<br>接入成就系统，20+探索或解谜类成就，等你收集！<br>还有神秘彩蛋，期待你的发现！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/5a22290068c132ed86de027c353e9f81.avif?t=1680426984\" width=420 height=80 /></span><br>键盘： 上下左右=方向键   SHIFT+上下左右=加速跑   Z=确定   X=取消    F4=全屏    F5=重置游戏    长按确定键=快进对话<br>手柄： 上下左右=方向键   X+上下左右=加速跑          A=确定    B=取消    Y=菜单    长按确定键=快进对话<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/903150/extras/ee71389872de4d5014e4ecaef386edb8.avif?t=1680426984\" width=420 height=80 /></span><br>什么？卡关了？来！小伙伴们一起解决！<br>朵游游戏交流群（QQ）：4141754<br>幻想曲制作组群（QQ）：544907793<br><br>更多活动！更多福利！<br>新浪微博：@朵游社<br>新浪微博：@幻想曲制作组<br><br>卡牌：根据steam新政策，卡牌会在游戏发行后达到一定的指标后掉落。",
